content: jvelasquez: Opened two refactoring PRs (#4019 and #4018) focused on removing submodules, with PR #4019 specifically targeting "unneeded submodules and workflow" and PR #4018 removing the "characters submodule." The refactoring work involved modest code changes across 18 files (+0/-4 lines), primarily affecting configuration files (78%) and tests (11%), with activity concentrated on a single day this week.
